data.description: Don't miss this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome located in Northlake. It features a primary bedroom on the main with a private ensuite bathroom. This home boasts an open floor plan with a nice dining area and a cozy family room that has tall ceilings and a gas fireplace. The kitchen and adjacent laundry room complete the main level. Upstairs, there's a nice open loft space, two more bedrooms, and a shared hall bathroom. The lot backs up to a wooded area for extra privacy. Conveniently located near I-77, I-485, Northlake Mall, shopping and restaurants. Schedule your showing today before it’s gone.
